MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 746

RESERVING A PARCEL OF FORESHORE LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN IN ARGAO, CEBU FOR PUBLIC USE, ENJOYMENT AND BEACH RESORT PURPOSES

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL ARROYO , President of the Republic of the Philippines, do hereby withdraw from any disposition, either through sale, lease or settlement and reserve for public use, enjoyment and for beach resort purposes under the administration of the Municipality of Argao, Cebu, a certain parcel of foreshore land of the public domain situated from the corner of National Highway and Rizal Streets at Lo-oc, Poblacion, Argao, Cebu up to the Argao River, subject to private rights, if any there and to final survey, which parcel of foreshore land is more particularly described as follows:

