Prior clearance from, and/or approval of, the Cebu Port Authority shall be required in the construction of any port or port-related structures and in the conduct of any cargo-handling activities in the reserved area.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF , I hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

DONE in the City of Manila, this 13th day of December in the year of Our Lord, Two Thousand and Four.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) EDUARDO R. ERMITA Executive Secretary

